org.eclipse.eef

Interface EEFListDescription

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EEFControlDescription, EEFWidgetDescription, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EEFListDescriptionImpl

    public interface EEFListDescription
extends EEFWidgetDescription
    A representation of the model object 'EEF List Description'. Represents a list in the user interface.

    The following features are supported:

    • Value Expression
    • Display Expression
    • On Click Expression
    • Actions
    • Style
    • Conditional Styles
    See Also:
    EefPackage.getEEFListDescription()
